{"tid":871820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國赴北海道旅客帶香腸入境　驗出非洲豬瘟","createTime":"2018-10-22T09:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T03:52:12.000Z","uid":75969,"like":402,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"af4078b1f3c784f22cf0bb91ab62bdc412ec6e39","tid":871820,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181022/photo/bkn-20181022154754721-1022_00912_001_01p.jpg?20181022160356\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181022%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181022154754721-1022_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20181022160356&h=09abc66d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國爆發非洲豬瘟疫情並持續擴散。（互聯網）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n日本農林水產省周一（22日）表示，有由中國至北海道新千歲機場的旅客欲把香腸帶入日本境內，當局在香腸驗出對非洲豬瘟呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n中國早前爆發非洲豬瘟疫情並持續擴散，死亡率幾乎是100%，人類不會受到感染。在日本，則至今未確認有豬隻感染個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181022/bkn-20181022154754721-1022_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181022%2Fbkn-20181022154754721-1022_00912_001.html&d=ax1iBzcBQBHgfFlmKBArgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=39d58f0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181022/bkn-20181022154754721-1022_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n支那又想送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ed20cc30b93ccee1f7ea16e3f030146b129bc8","tid":871820,"uid":52006,"like":204,"dislike":0,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"擺明想將瘟疫輸出去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c25f3a655a7e1d258170d940b4a6ed44115efe","tid":871820,"uid":67065,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"即係有豬瘟既豬都拎左黎整野食"},{"pid":"ad5613210ed073a3d9351575978344ecf7ebe092","tid":871820,"uid":82162,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score